00:50:45.710 --> 00:50:51.470
aren't those rules, because
there isn't a nuclear family

00:50:51.470 --> 00:50:56.300
to keep younger kids today from
growing up and being just

00:50:56.300 --> 00:50:58.120
like those that are
around them?

00:50:58.120 --> 00:50:59.920
So how do you stop that?

00:50:59.920 --> 00:51:01.820
Because I couldn't agree with
you more on the drug

00:51:01.820 --> 00:51:03.190
conversation.

00:51:03.190 --> 00:51:07.290
But how do you educate
them all together?

00:51:07.290 --> 00:51:12.040
CARL HART: Now, I should tell
